				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The player has dug up a body that looks particularly messy/bloody/scarred. For anyone else, this is just a simple \"Ew\" moment to question why you're going digging.  But for the Dark urge, they remember and are happy with it, which prompts a PAD that follows this up."
